extends ../layout

block content
  .pb-2.mt-2.mb-4.border-bottom


    h3 Propose an SCD Clinic
    p Community is inherently diverse.  An SCD Hub clinic need not be formally organized. Simply by expressing your own unique perspective on a design, planning, or cultural issue in your community, your words and reseach can influence entire project outcomes.

    p Please think of how the information your clinic uncovers will be useful to others.    SCD Clinics are successful when the people participating gain a better undersanding.  Informed public discussion leads to better desision making powers.   As a US non profit organization, SCD Hub can provide a letter of support for your SCD Clinic, helpful when requesting free public meeting spaces, outreach & promotion, etc.


    form(id='cinicsignup-form', method='POST', action='/signup', onsubmit='if(document.getElementById(\'agree\').checked) { return true; } else { alert(\'Please indicate that you have read and agree to the Terms and Conditions and Privacy Policy\'); return false; }')

    input(type='hidden', name='_csrf', value=_csrf)
    .form-group.row
      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='email') Email
      .col-md-7
        input.form-control(type='email', name='email', id='email', placeholder='Email', autofocus, required)
    .form-group.row
      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='password') Password
      .col-md-7
        input.form-control(type='password', name='password', id='password', placeholder='Password', minlength='8', required)
    .form-group.row
      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='confirmPassword') Confirm Password
      .col-md-7
        input.form-control(type='password', name='confirmPassword', id='confirmPassword', placeholder='Confirm Password', minlength='8', required)


    .form-group.row
      .col-md-3 
      .col-md-7
        img(src='/captcha')
    .form-group.row
      label.col-md-3.col-form-label.font-weight-bold.text-right(for='confirmPassword') Type captcha or refresh
      .col-md-7
          input.form-control(type='text', name='captcha', id='captcha')


    .form-group.row
      .col-md-3 
      .col-md-7
        input#agree(type='checkbox', name='checkbox', value='check')
        |  I have read and agree to the
        br
        a(href='/terms') Terms and Conditions
        |  and 
        a(href='/privacy') Privacy Policy

    .form-group.offset-sm-3.col-md-7.pl-2
      button.btn.btn-success(type='submit')
        i.fas.fa-user-plus.fa-sm
        | Lets do this
